<ProductLayout {title} heading="Garages & Carports" {description} {images} {faqs}>
  <div class="text-xl">
    <p>Oak-framed garages and carports built to suit your property, single or double, open or enclosed, with workshop space or log storage built in where you need it. Call <strong>01228 512303</strong> to discuss your requirements.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Offer</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list mb-2">
      <li>Double garages and single garages</li>
